How to Fix Minimal BASH Like Line Editing is Supported GRUB Error In Linux
grub >ls //step-1
grub >ls (hd0,gpt3)   //ext*4  //step-2
grub >set root=(hd0,gpt3) //step-3
grub >set prefix=(hd0,gpt3)/boot/grub
grub >insmod normal //setp-4
grub >normal


then....
sudo grub-install /dev/sda3
sudo update-grub
